{"tid":1867284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不如諗下依家中共港共最驚乜嘢 我地可以做啲乜嘢","createTime":"2020-02-07T06:15:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T08:11:19.000Z","uid":57786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"09eba663d4acc29565688f99dfa79582c229dc7c","tid":1867284,"uid":57786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T06:15:33.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎呢單嘢百年一遇<br />\n俾中共港共捱到我地就等收皮<br />\n<br />\n木木鄭一直助攻我地<br />\n可能因為要中共收咗皮<br />\n佢先唔使俾人要脅<br />\n<br />\n今次佢叫大家唔好戴口罩<br />\n又唔肯封關<br />\n佢要做嘅都做晒<br />\n<br />\n你班戇鳩唔係仲要戴口罩出街呀麻"},{"pid":"eeb58ba8131aec9dd256722ff8af8be4fd0ef81b","tid":1867284,"uid":57786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T06:15:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a22b0ebe74c660e40b6f77a930c61a598a5e5e0","tid":1867284,"uid":57786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T06:17:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9a36af9eae557989dd561b0592510edfb4079c1","tid":1867284,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T06:23:12.000Z","msg":"最驚冇得返工"},{"pid":"f7b55d73772035f3beeb03ae0bb8ae4579ca61fb","tid":1867284,"uid":332804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T06:25:43.000Z","msg":"最驚股市大跌/run唔到﹐只有向中共送錢先係港共真春袋。"},{"pid":"ccfdc78baef29d429e16132c5103eda332bdad45","tid":1867284,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T06:27:23.000Z","msg":"中共 應該話所有霸權最怕就係人民起義 軍隊叛變<br />\n所以上大陸網幫手吹風係一個唔錯既選擇<br />\n<br />\n港共 我諗就怕中共倒台掛<br />\n基本上港共政府都唔怕全部港人死光光<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb75037c7b530fb6e0dde04b67196b1d33208b7d","tid":1867284,"uid":205462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T06:40:10.000Z","msg":"中共當然最怕係香港之後無新嘅確診個案，而上海，深圳呢啲經濟中心就肺炎爆到仆街啦<br />\n<br />\n大劣都有搵水車噴消毒液洗街啦，咁香港呢? 食環外判商都因為幾個月無糧出，就快要停工了"},{"pid":"4e88dd